{"name":"Manila → Camino → Manila","currency_note":"Booking links use date-flexible search. Replace dates in the URL once set.","items":[{"id":"mnl-dxb-out","type":"flight","icon":"✈️","from":"Manila (MNL)","to":"Dubai (DXB)","duration":"~9h","carriers":["Emirates","Cebu Pacific"],"note":"Long-haul leg out. Most flights are red-eye departures from MNL.","options":[{"label":"Search Google Flights","url":"https://www.google.com/travel/flights?q=Flights%20from%20MNL%20to%20DXB"},{"label":"Search Skyscanner","url":"https://www.skyscanner.com.ph/transport/flights/mnl/dxb/"},{"label":"Emirates direct","url":"https://www.emirates.com"}]},{"id":"dxb-layover-out","type":"layover","icon":"🛬","at":"Dubai (DXB)","note":"Transit layover. DXB Terminals 3 has showers, prayer rooms, and a quiet zone. Stretch your legs before the next leg."},{"id":"dxb-mad","type":"flight","icon":"✈️","from":"Dubai (DXB)","to":"Madrid (MAD)","duration":"~8h","carriers":["Emirates"],"note":"Direct flight, usually arrives Madrid in the late afternoon.","options":[{"label":"Search Google Flights","url":"https://www.google.com/travel/flights?q=Flights%20from%20DXB%20to%20MAD"},{"label":"Search Skyscanner","url":"https://www.skyscanner.com.ph/transport/flights/dxb/mad/"},{"label":"Emirates direct","url":"https://www.emirates.com"}]},{"id":"city-madrid","type":"city","icon":"🏛️","name":"Madrid","note":"Spain's capital. Recover from the flight, see a museum, eat well.","highlights":["Museo del Prado (Velázquez, Goya, Bosch)","Reina Sofía (Guernica)","Plaza Mayor & Mercado de San Miguel","Retiro Park","Tapas in La Latina or Malasaña","Royal Palace & Almudena Cathedral"]},{"id":"mad-vgo","type":"transit","icon":"🚄","from":"Madrid","to":"Vigo","duration":"Train ~4h, Plane ~1h 25m, Bus ~8h","note":"Train is the most pleasant; plane is fastest door-to-door once you add airport time.","options":[{"label":"Renfe Alvia train (~4h, €40-80)","url":"https://www.renfe.com/es/en/travel"},{"label":"Iberia / Vueling flig