rera)","Barri Gòtic (gothic quarter)","La Boqueria market","Barceloneta beach","Tapas, vermut, pa amb tomàquet","FC Barcelona at Camp Nou (if in season)"]},{"id":"bcn-dxb","type":"flight","icon":"✈️","from":"Barcelona (BCN)","to":"Dubai (DXB)","duration":"~7h","carriers":["Emirates"],"note":"Direct flight, usually overnight from Barcelona.","options":[{"label":"Search Google Flights","url":"https://www.google.com/travel/flights?q=Flights%20from%20BCN%20to%20DXB"},{"label":"Search Skyscanner","url":"https://www.skyscanner.com.ph/transport/flights/bcn/dxb/"},{"label":"Emirates direct","url":"https://www.emirates.com"}]},{"id":"dxb-layover-ret","type":"layover","icon":"🛬","at":"Dubai (DXB)","note":"Return transit. Stretch, shower, eat something before the long leg home."},{"id":"dxb-mnl-ret","type":"flight","icon":"✈️","from":"Dubai (DXB)","to":"Manila (MNL)","duration":"~9h","carriers":["Emirates","Cebu Pacific"],"note":"Home.","options":[{"label":"Search Google Flights","url":"https://www.google.com/travel/flights?q=Flights%20from%20DXB%20to%20MNL"},{"label":"Search Skyscanner","url":"https://www.skyscanner.com.ph/transport/flights/dxb/mnl/"},{"label":"Emirates direct","url":"https://www.emirates.com"}]}]}